    <properties>
        <title>Copy NOTICE and LICENSE files to javadoc jar</title>
        <author email="dev@commons.apache.org">Apache Commons Documentation Team</author>
    </properties>

    <body>

        <section name="Copy NOTICE and LICENSE files to javadoc jar">

            <p>
            This <i>mojo</i> (or <i>ant build script</i>) currently copies
            the NOTICE and LICENSE files to target/apidocs so that they are included in the
            generated -javadoc.jar. This is currently done in the commons-parent pom.xml
            using the antrun plugin. Doing it here removes the need to have ant script in
            commons-parent.
            </p>

            <p>
            See:
            </p>
